{"tid":1780236,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2019日本年度漢字「令」：令和元年跨越災難的時代想望","createTime":"2019-12-12T08:12:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T08:24:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c99f6af0382d65945b4087db6fae8ac0bf4ad953","tid":1780236,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:12:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2019/12/12/99/7185597.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1140\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2019%2F12%2F12%2F99%2F7185597.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1140&h=23a87b40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 令和時代第一個年度漢字就是「令」！日本2019年的年度漢字票選結果今天出爐，從21萬票中脫穎而出的年度漢字是「令」，正如事前外界的預測，做為新年號「令和」象徵的選字是今年的大熱門，除了意指2019年新天皇即位、日本走入新時代的國民想望之外，也做為跨越去年度的「災」字、平撫傷痛的期許。<br />\n<br />\n年度漢字在12日下午於京都清水寺奧之院公開發表，現年79歲的清水寺住持森清範，照往年慣例在特大型的和紙上大筆揮毫，寫下今年度票選結果的漢字。今年度募集總數共有216,365張票選，比起去年成長1萬多票；「令」字以30,427高票（14.07%）脫穎而出，打敗第二名「新」（1萬4,850票）、第三名「和」（1萬281票），成為今年度2019年、同時也是新年號令和時代的第一個代表漢字。<br />\n<br />\n 「令」除了意指年號令和之外，也有呼應日本今年消費稅率調漲等諸多「法令改正」、以及今年因應天災的各種避難勸告「警報令」（発「令」）。今年度的漢字也特別由日本niconico平台直播，不過當結果出爐的瞬間，卻也有許多網友感慨「令」字沒什麼驚喜，「根本毫無意外」，甚至還有人說「國語力低下？」不過就事前的各家預測來看，「令」確實是本屆的熱門候選。<br />\n<br />\n2019年對於日本來說，同時也是跨越平成、迎接新時代令和的重要起始。4月1日公布了新年號「令和」、到5月1日的德仁天皇即位，對於嶄新未來的想望，也就自然流露在年度漢字的熱門候選「令」、「和」以及「新」字之上。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4221587\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.udn.com%2Fglobal_vision%2Fstory%2F8662%2F4221587&d=Vh0AUGqI%2BhuKY3uG7C8Fc4Mqd%2FJDLPQOR3COl2rYgn0%3D&h=6da90bd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://global.udn.com/global_vision/story/8662/4221587</a>"},{"pid":"01e89aa2f5cdecc8bbc2c23c35cb40eb8713caa7","tid":1780236,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/09/03/100416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F09%2F03%2F100416_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c943f518&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7584eecf64763c3eb350fa8384f9949bf3211758","tid":1780236,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"巧令令"},{"pid":"ab7346cecd0a23920335c3beba1d9c71fa980e4a","tid":1780236,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7584eecf64763c3eb350fa8384f9949bf3211758","tid":1780236,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"巧令令"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"架仔好多5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaeabfabe75087f15ab3a6270bf4e8758df30918","tid":1780236,"uid":61372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab7346cecd0a23920335c3beba1d9c71fa980e4a","tid":1780236,"uid":69568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7584eecf64763c3eb350fa8384f9949bf3211758","tid":1780236,"uid":46155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"巧令令"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:15:16.000Z","msg":"架仔好多5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T08:24:36.000Z","msg":"收嗲啦usb"}]}